TdhBxi7p8", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66826}, {"id": 225803, "content": "爱笑的女孩都幸运", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091592}, {"id": 104715, "content": "感觉身体被掏空", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 516779}, {"id": 105227, "content": "新媒体从业者每天都接触这些，正是这些恶心的词让我想离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705840}, {"id": 104716, "content": "不转不是中国人，中国人都转了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704634}, {"id": 104972, "content": "转了第二天必有好事", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 601634}, {"id": 105484, "content": "赞多出原图or …靠自己能力怎么怎么滴", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607959}, {"id": 104717, "content": "且行且珍惜", "image": null, "praise_count": 61, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703665}, {"id": 105229, "content": "男儿有泪不轻弹", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343597}, {"id": 104718, "content": " 老司机带带我，呜呜的小火车开起来！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704634}, {"id": 104974, "content": "我得了穷癌，只有钱才能治好我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705193}, {"id": 105486, "content": "你知道他有多努力吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693319}, {"id": 104719, "content": "你开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 704146}, {"id": 104975, "content": "长得好看的已点赞，丑的人还在犹豫。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 705201}, {"id": 104720, "content": "以大多数人的努力程度之低，根本轮不到拼天赋", "image": null, "praise_count": 88, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 697909}, {"id": 104976, "content": "人要活得有意义，不然还不如挂掉", "image": "img/option/option/20160806170441VMJvet04HEi9dQaX", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691760}, {"id": 104721, "content": "可能是空间非主流们矫情的话。", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 693981}, {"id": 104977, "content": "你开心就好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668967}, {"id": 105233, "content": "谁的青春不迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703559}, {"id": 106769, "content": "别爱得太满，别睡得太晚。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 570869}, {"id": 104978, "content": "学习使我快乐 ?（我不学习时更快乐啊哈哈哈）", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 500722}]}